snippet.title: Retrieval Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
The Future Games Show at Gamescom wrapped up with a world premiere trailer for Retrieval, 333 Studios' cinematic horror adventure. It's coming soon, but you can wishlist it now on Steam.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#Retrieval #FutureGamesShow #FGS
